00:29:14.295 --> 00:29:20.187
we would have had no beauty about us, isn’t it? There would have been no variety,

00:29:20.295 --> 00:29:24.187
such a boring thing to see, all these chairs morning till evening.

00:29:24.295 --> 00:29:31.187
