But a saint is the other way round. When he sees others in pain, then the compassion fills him completely.

01:17:26.295 --> 01:17:32.187
and you can see the compassion from those eyes, absolutely the same terrific eyes become so compassionate

01:17:32.295 --> 01:17:39.187
that you are surprised that how this love is flowing. And at the same time he can take a hunter in his hand and hit people;

01:17:39.295 --> 01:17:44.187
at the same time he can be very wrathful with people who try to destroy the saints,

01:17:44.295 --> 01:17:50.187
he can be extremely wrathful, and he can be very, very, very, very dynamic.

01:17:50.295 --> 01:18:01.187
He can be anything; but he uses it for the purpose of one thing: is to save the saints and to make them the Spirit.

01:18:01.295 --> 01:18:07.187
His only concern is how to make them the Spirit, and for that how to save them.

01:18:07.295 --> 01:18:15.187
For that, whatever has to do – sometimes it can act like a tigress, just jump on people

01:18:15.295 --> 01:18:24.187
who try to be injurious, or try to be sort of harmful to the children of the tigress.

01:18:24.295 --> 01:18:30.187
Or it can become so mild, so mild: I don’t know if you have seen a crocodile giving bath to her children.

01:18:30.295 --> 01:18:35.187
Her eyes become absolutely so mild, imagine. It’s like that.

01:18:35.295 --> 01:18:43.187
That love you start seeing in a person who is a saint and who becomes a realized soul,

01:18:43.295 --> 01:18:47.187
that he feels for others. Not for himself. He is not bothered!

01:18:47.295 --> 01:18:54.187
Comforts do not matter – where you sit, what you need, “I must have this food”: that all nonsense, never comes in the mind.

01:18:54.295 --> 01:19:00.187
What matters is: “Oh God, what’s happening to these people, these are my children!

01:19:00.295 --> 01:19:05.187
They are seekers, they are saints, they have been seeking for thousands of years.

01:19:05.295 --> 01:19:13.187
How am I to save them?”. And such people who are dry they end up in heart attacks, and another is paralysis.

01:19:13.295 --> 01:19:17.187
I mean, you should never have sympathies for people who have heart troubles.

01:19:17.295 --> 01:19:23.187
Tell them to be more loving. Spend some time with your wife. Spend some time with your children. You see,

01:19:23.295 --> 01:19:31.187
mostly these busy people are those who are at the helm of affairs, who think that the whole world will be drowned without them.

01:19:31.295 --> 01:19:39.187
Actually with them it may be drowned, I don’t know about that part. Such very busy people, you see,

01:19:39.295 --> 01:19:49.187
who have no time to waste in their family and who are holding the banner of some sort of a great thing so-called – t

01:19:49.295 --> 01:19:57.187
hey always get heart attacks and die. If they are not shot off, they are – they get their own heart attacks and die.

01:19:57.295 --> 01:20:05.187
They get – can get even epilepsy, but it’s not actually the epilepsy – it looks like epilepsy

01:20:05.295 --> 01:20:17.187
but it is a kind of a failure of the part of the head which is on this, the ego side.

01:20:17.295 --> 01:20:27.187
And a person can get paralyzed or he may become absolutely without any sensation in his body.

01:20:27.295 --> 01:20:33.187
These people, till they die they are very alert, their brain is very alert, despite the fact they have used their brain.

01:20:33.295 --> 01:20:41.187
Actually the nature is very balanced; they have used their brain, with their brain only they have achieved whatever they wanted to,

01:20:41.295 --> 01:20:46.187
but their brain is alert, but their heart goes out, the balance comes in.

01:20:46.295 --> 01:20:52.187
But if you have used your heart too much, the left side as it is, too much of crying and weeping and this and that and all that,

01:20:52.295 --> 01:21:00.187
you become – on the contrary your heart going out, your brain goes out. The balance is established.

01:21:00.295 --> 01:21:06.187
It’s surprising, that people said that in the mental hospital no use having a cardiogram.

01:21:06.295 --> 01:21:11.187
There’s no need because you don’t need it. Their heart is perfect.

01:21:11.295 --> 01:21:14.187
While they use their heart all the time, the brain goes out.

01:21:14.295 --> 01:21:21.187
And you become a brainless person or a gaga person, I don’t know all sorts of things that people get.

01:21:21.295 --> 01:21:26.187
So one has to understand that a balance is brought about by this position,

01:21:26.295 --> 01:21:31.187
and that’s why Buddha has said “Keep in the center. Do not go to extremes”.

01:21:31.295 --> 01:21:35.187
When you go into extremes, this moves in the periphery.

01:21:35.295 --> 01:21:41.187
Supposing you are a thinker and you plan everything and you are meticulous, and this and that,

01:21:41.295 --> 01:21:43.187
you are thrown out of the way.

01:21:43.295 --> 01:21:50.187
Now, the extreme thing of this could create a very egoistical supra-conscious spirit in you.

01:21:50.295 --> 01:22:00.187
The one who we can cite was Mr. Hitler. Mr. Hitler was nothing else but a person who lived in the collective supra-conscious.

01:22:00.295 --> 01:22:07.187
And he charmed people by his collective consciousness – collective supra-consciousness.

01:22:07.295 --> 01:22:15.187
What he did is to talk so big and so nonsensical things, if you read his lectures you’ll be amazed,

01:22:15.295 --> 01:22:24.187
that he said that: “We are the Germans, we are the special race, we are this and we should kill all these people”, and people believed it!

01:22:24.295 --> 01:22:32.187
It was just a possession, a collective possession. I mean, if you talk to those Germans now, I read some articles written by them,

01:22:32.295 --> 01:22:39.187
really they can’t understand, they said, “We were young people, we were studying, we were students, we were very good people,

01:22:39.295 --> 01:22:47.187
and suddenly all this came up to us and he built us up as some sort of a martyr and all that, and we took to it”.

01:22:47.295 --> 01:22:53.187
He made it such a big religious stuff, I mean, a fanatic thing in their head, that they accepted it.

01:22:53.295 --> 01:22:59.187
This is the extreme case of fanaticism. All the fanatics are on this side. All of them are on this side.

01:22:59.295 --> 01:23:05.187
Any fanaticism I am facing. Keep away from them. They are headaches, they are bores, numbering bores.

01:23:05.295 --> 01:23:11.187
You just can’t talk to them. All the fanatics of the world if they were bores it’s all right,

01:23:11.295 --> 01:23:17.187
but they go much beyond that. Like you see Khomeini’s there. He is a good example of fanaticism.

01:23:17.295 --> 01:23:29.187
And what – I’m happy that Americans had a little experience of these fanatics. All fanatics catch all these people.

01:23:29.295 --> 01:23:36.187
These so-called Lutherans, and the so-called Pentecostal, they are nothing but they are all possessed people –

01:23:36.295 --> 01:23:40.187
specially the Pentecostals are possessed, can’t you see them?

01:23:40.295 --> 01:23:43.187
They are recluses, they are useless people, they are wasting themselves.

01:23:43.295 --> 01:23:51.187
All the spiritualists and all these people – they could be right-sided or left-sided.

01:23:51.295 --> 01:23:59.187
LSD takes you to the right side, because you start seeing the lights and all those hallucinations which are of the supra-conscious.

01:23:59.295 --> 01:24:06.187
Left-sided people who are there, they get into – they are all the time crying, weeping,

01:24:06.295 --> 01:24:12.187
diffident, sly type, intriguers, they are on the left hand side.

01:24:12.295 --> 01:24:15.187
But if you move too much on this side then you can also get possessed.

01:24:15.295 --> 01:24:21.187
You can get very badly possessed and this one, this movement is very painful.

01:24:21.295 --> 01:24:24.187
Is painful to the person. Because they aggress on the person.

01:24:24.295 --> 01:24:32.187
But if you have this kind, this type of movement on the right hand side, then you aggress others.

01:24:32.295 --> 01:24:36.187
Because this is done with the ego and this is done with the superego.

01:24:36.295 --> 01:24:48.187
So the person who has a left side problem is better in the society because he troubles himself, and he needs his own cure, and he is not a problem.

01:24:48.295 --> 01:24:55.187
But a person who is a egoist is such a problem that he doesn’t see, he doesn’t feel the pain of others and he gives pain to others.

01:24:55.295 --> 01:25:01.187
He talks in such a way that he hurts, and he has a very bad right Vishuddhi,

01:25:01.295 --> 01:25:07.187
and everything he does, all aggressiveness, all war and all these things are a right-sided man.

01:25:07.295 --> 01:25:14.187
And such a man can become very successful like Hitler, but ultimately he meets his doom

01:25:14.295 --> 01:25:22.187
and nobody respects such a person ultimately. See, everything afterwards in history tells about the dirty things he was doing,

01:25:22.295 --> 01:25:27.187
the sly things he was doing, or the bad things he was doing, how many he has killed,

01:25:27.295 --> 01:25:34.187
what he did – everything comes out in history and he is just put into the light of history,

01:25:34.295 --> 01:25:38.187
and you start seeing that this man, who was supposed to be so successful,

01:25:38.295 --> 01:25:43.187
“Oh, God, we do not want to know him”. One of the sahaja yogis came to Me,

01:25:43.295 --> 01:25:49.187
he told Me – he’s a French – he said, “Mother, please tell me if I was Napoleon. If I was don’t tell me,

01:25:49.295 --> 01:25:57.187
because then I will die”. I said, “Why?”. He said, “I feel that I’m very egoistical, after Realization

01:25:57.295 --> 01:26:04.187
I find my ego is like this and I topple like that, and I can draw very well, and he used to draw.

01:26:04.295 --> 01:26:09.187
So if I was Napoleon don’t tell me, if I was don’t tell me, I will really commit suicide”.

01:26:09.295 --> 01:26:14.187
And in French, in French people if you call somebody a Napoleon, it’s a, it’s an abuse,

01:26:14.295 --> 01:26:20.187
you can imagine, Napoleon the great is being used as an abuse.

01:26:20.295 --> 01:26:25.187
So this is the thing that one has to understand, that ego-oriented person is over-disciplined,

01:26:25.295 --> 01:26:33.187
may be military-like, he may not drink, smoke, you see, he may walk straight like a stick. But he is old.

01:26:33.295 --> 01:26:39.187
The other one might be indulging into all such things and he might be drinking too much,

01:26:39.295 --> 01:26:44.187
and all the drunkards you find are on the left hand side. Poor things they start with a small thing.

01:26:44.295 --> 01:26:49.187
When they start it with a small thing they are driven onto this extreme, then they get caught up.

01:26:49.295 --> 01:26:55.187
Alcoholics are really, not that they drink, there’s some spirit in them that drinks.

01:26:55.295 --> 01:27:02.187
I met last time a lady from Cuba, she was a petite woman, small, thin woman, and her husband came

01:27:02.295 --> 01:27:08.187
and told Me that she can take one whisky bottle neat! I said: “This little woman, how does she do it?!”.

01:27:08.295 --> 01:27:13.187
He said: “She does!”. And I asked her and she said: “Yes, Mother, I do”.

01:27:13.295 --> 01:27:17.187
I put her a bandhan and I found a horrible big personality in her.

01:27:17.295 --> 01:27:22.187
Horrible, tall, very hefty person. He said, “Mother, did you see that one?”.

01:27:22.295 --> 01:27:27.187
I said: “Yes, I did”. She said, “It is he who drinks, and I’m blamed”. She could see him also.

01:27:27.295 --> 01:27:33.187
Such people who are on the left side can see the spirits and the things walking in,

01:27:33.295 --> 01:27:39.187
and they get all kinds of ESP experiences, and “I get a hunch” and all sorts of things – is little movement that side.

01:27:39.295 --> 01:27:44.187
And the right-sided people also can have such hunches as to what to do tomorrow,

01:27:44.295 --> 01:27:49.187
and how to do it, and what will happen, they get all kinds of hunches.

01:27:49.295 --> 01:27:56.187
There are people who are getting photographs of the people, such people – one gentleman showed Me some photographs

01:27:56.295 --> 01:28:06.187
which in an organization in (…). It’s a lady, she showed Me it’s taking out the photographs of all the horrible kings of England.

01:28:06.295 --> 01:28:13.187
As if they were dead, with their faces… it was surprising! It was surprising.

01:28:13.295 --> 01:28:18.187
And now thank God that organization is not getting any information, but it was a horrible thing, and

01:28:18.295 --> 01:28:24.187
if you keep these photographs in your house you also get bad vibrations, you might get their spirits coming into you.

01:28:24.295 --> 01:28:30.187
In BBC the other day we saw a film where a man was possessed by a spirit of Van Gogh.

01:28:30.295 --> 01:28:37.187
I hope you know him, Van Gogh is the painter who paints in one line many colors like that, you see?

01:28:37.295 --> 01:28:42.187
And this fellow was doing – actually I mean, we saw that with our own eyes – was painting just like Van Gogh.

01:28:42.295 --> 01:28:46.187
And he said that, “Van Gogh is doing this to me”.

01:28:46.295 --> 01:28:51.187
So all such things happen when you are on the left side – could be on the right side,

01:28:51.295 --> 01:28:57.187
for some artist may be on the right side. But this you can only find out with vibrations, which side you are possessed.

01:28:57.295 --> 01:29:03.187
Now I’ve told you why we have to have dharma, why we have to have Ten Commandments,

01:29:03.295 --> 01:29:08.187
why we should be in our sustenance, so that we keep to the middle path of Sushumna,

01:29:08.295 --> 01:29:17.187
this center path of our evolution, and not to deviate too much to this side and not to deviate too much to that side.

01:29:17.295 --> 01:29:24.187
That’s the reason we had to have religions. But all religions have become fanatics. They are fanatics.

01:29:24.295 --> 01:29:27.187
So they are good for nothing, useless people.

01:29:27.295 --> 01:29:33.187
Absolutely on the contrary they have created so many sects and so many fightings that one can’t understand.

01:29:33.295 --> 01:29:39.187
Now, these great Incarnations have come on this earth, they all have come as one aspect.

01:29:39.295 --> 01:29:44.187
Christ has said “Those who are not against Me – with Me”.Who are those who are not against Him?

01:29:44.295 --> 01:29:52.187
See, you didn’t even allow Him to talk! He had to fight for every-day life!

01:29:52.295 --> 01:29:56.187
Same thing you did to Mohammed Sahib, the same thing you did to all the saints who came on this earth.

01:29:56.295 --> 01:30:00.187
It’s not only Christ, you see the life of Socrates.

01:30:00.295 --> 01:30:08.187
You see the life of everyone who was like this, we had Sai Nath in India, was only hundred years back he must have died, only hundred years back.

01:30:08.295 --> 01:30:12.187
But if you see His life was a struggle! Nobody would listen to Him.

01:30:12.295 --> 01:30:20.187
At least there are some people here to listen to Me, but Sai Nath had about three or four disciples, that’s all.

01:30:20.295 --> 01:30:26.187
That is the sign that I must be a true Teacher, because if you have too much that means you are all mesmerized,

01:30:26.295 --> 01:30:35.187
and thousands, fifty-thousand people are sitting there and somebody is throwing a red colour through a cannon and they are “ah!”, like mad.

01:30:35.295 --> 01:30:42.187
Is this God’s Realization? Is this spirituality? You are not to be mad people.

01:30:42.295 --> 01:30:48.187
You have to be aware, and specially alert. You become really aware,

01:30:48.295 --> 01:30:52.187
which is enlightened, your awareness has to be enlightened, you have to become that.

01:30:52.295 --> 01:30:56.187
Not to be like sheep, go there into any place, taken away anywhere – no, not that.

01:30:56.295 --> 01:31:02.187
So we have to awaken ourselves. We have to brighten ourselves and understand our responsibility.

01:31:02.295 --> 01:31:08.187
And we have to know that we are saints, we have come here to become our Spirits,

01:31:08.295 --> 01:31:13.187
and the responsibility is very much great on the people of America.

01:31:13.295 --> 01:31:20.187
American saints have the greatest responsibility, though Sahaja Yoga has prospered so much in Australia. Most surprising.

01:31:20.295 --> 01:31:25.187
You condemned them as criminals, they went down there, they had children, grand-children,

01:31:25.295 --> 01:31:34.187
and they have much less ego, much more wisdom, and that is the center of Mooladhara.

01:31:34.295 --> 01:31:41.187
That is the first center. Australia is the first center. And people are so wise, you won’t believe.

01:31:41.295 --> 01:31:47.187
I mean, there was not even a single seat left when I went there, and thousands of people,

01:31:47.295 --> 01:31:51.187
the media was so sensible and so wise, and – I mean, there are seven cities

01:31:51.295 --> 01:31:58.187
and all the seven cities have got centers in Sahaja Yoga. Just like villagers in India; they are so wise.

01:31:58.295 --> 01:32:02.187
As villagers in India are wise, they are that wise. And I don’t know what to say:

01:32:02.295 --> 01:32:06.187
the persons who are supposed to be the complete wisdom here at this point, to be the witness,

01:32:06.295 --> 01:32:12.187
to be the sixteens – can you see here [points at Vishuddhi on chakra chart – ed], sub-sixteen, and I’ll talk about it next time,

01:32:12.295 --> 01:32:18.187
because I’ve told you about this center of Rama and then I’ll tell you about all these centers tomorrow, and above also.

