01:33:46.295 --> 01:33:55.187
it’s the things you have come out of it, and what was your education, how were your parents – I mean,

01:33:55.295 --> 01:34:02.187
so many things work it out, the personality. And these three gunas, tamo, rajo and sattwa gunas,

01:34:02.295 --> 01:34:08.187
